name: Ki-Adi-Mundi (V)
Lore: 'Cerean Jedi trained by Yoda since the age of four. Only Jedi Council member who is a Jedi Knight. Freed his homeworld from a group of rogues without any bloodshed.',
Text: 'While Maul present, Ki-Adi-Mundi is Heroic.  Obi-wan''s Cape, Obi-wan''s Journal, and [Virtual Block 5] Jedi Lightsaber may deploy on Ki-Adi-Mundi.  Once per game, may exchange two cards from hand with any one card in Lost Pile.',
